---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Stefano De Checchi" description="A bit about me.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <article
      class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none
        prose-headings:font-semibold
        prose-a:text-sage-700 dark:prose-a:text-sage-400"
    >
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Stefano De Checchi. I live in [City] and care about two things: reducing harm in the world
        and building good software.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've been vegan since [year]. I write about the ethics, practicalities, and everyday joy of
        plant-based living — not to convert anyone, but because thinking out loud helps me understand
        what I actually believe.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also work as a software engineer, primarily in Go. I write about programming when I run
        into something worth sharing — a pattern that clicked, a mistake worth avoiding, a tool I
        actually use.
      </p>
      <p>This site is where I think out loud. No comments, no tracking — just writing.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Reach me at <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a> or find me on
        <a href="https://github.com/stephanoumenos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >GitHub</a
        >.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
